ord focus  manual are available for use by students staff and the general public at both hourly and daily rates customers book online at the hertz  website or using the hertz  android and ios app where they can locate available vehicles and reserve them subject to a  preauthorization on the users credit or debit card  minute prior to the booking start time the customer is allowed access to the vehicle the access code will be sent by both email and sms which they can input on a pin entry panel located on the drivers side of the vehicle windshield alternatively if the user has been issued with one they can gain access using their rfid entry pass the keys to the vehicle are located on a tether beside the steering wheel and are only used to operate the engine ignition locking the vehicle during a booking session continues to be done via the pin entry pad leaving the keys attached to the tether at all times a fuel card or electric vehicle charging card is located in the sun visor and the cost of gasoline electricity or diesel is covered by hertz the user simply pays the permile charge regardless of how much fuel was purchased for example in the united kingdom there is no electric vehicle mileage charge a pmile charge in cars and pmile charge in vans all users are required to return the vehicle at the end of the booking on time clean inside and out empty and with at least a quarter tank of fuel failure to do so will result in penalties for the inconvenience to the next user simply wheelz and advantageedit for premerger history see advantage rent a car in  hertz launched subbrand simply wheelz to address economyminded and leisuremarket customers in orlando florida the subbrand was colocated within and utilized the fleet and other assets of the parent brand and channeled reservations and customerservice through a streamlined web frontend resembling those of lowcostcarrier airlines to its existing systems hertz outbid enterprise rentacar acquiring the assets of bankrupt advantage rent a car system in early  the simply wheelz subbrand and website were then rebranded as advantage rentacar on august   hertz announced that it agreed to sell the us advantage business to franchise services of north america and macquarie capital as a divestiture to receive regulatory approval of hertzs acquisition of dollar thrifty automotive group announced at the same time and to convert foreign advantage locations to the thrifty brand on december   advantage rent a car was acquired by macquarie capital advertisingedit let hertz put you in the driver’s seatedit in  the advertising firm of norman craig  kummel nck was selected as the new advertising agency for hertz nck developed the slogan “hertz puts you in the driver’s seat” which was first used commercially in september  nck quickly changed the wording to “let hertz put you in the driver’s seat” by october  popular a cappella quartet the hilos sang the hertz song for the commercials hertz used the line in the early s in print signs and television the series is listed as number  in the top  advertising campaigns of the th century by advertising age magazine john f kennedy assassinationedit hertz billboard on the texas school book depository roof in  a large billboard advertising hertz was on the roof of the texas school book depository in dealey plaza during the assassination of president john f kennedy on november   the billboard was removed in  oj simpsonedit oj simpson appeared prominently in ads for the company the company set the trend of hiring black athletes as sponsors of various brands in  oj simpson became a staple in american households with his hertz commercials one spot from the mids showed simpson former football star as he was running through an airport terminal wearing a threepiece business suit and carrying a briefcase and leaping over rows of departure lounge seats trying to get to his hertz rental car a woman yelled go oj go the tagline of the ad as spoken by oj was hertz the superstar in rentacar in later years and through the s he appeared with golf legend arnold palmer the pair was joined by the early s by actress jamie lee curtis the relationship between hertz and simpson ended in  following simpsons arrest for the murder of nicole brown simpson and ron goldman lowfloor passenger busedit a low floor hertz bus at ohare international airport in chicago a significant hertzled technology was the development in north america of the lowfloor passenger coach until the early st century most large hertz lots were linked to airports they served by small fleets of firmoperated transit buses many hertz locations used the rapid transit series whose high floor and stairs made loading of baggage difficult and rendered access to wheelchair and ecvusing customers difficult or impossible a large potential contract from hertz led gillig brothers of hayward california to invest in a radical redesign of the city bus that offered a floor only a foot off of the ground lower when pneumatically kneeled from the front of the bus between the front wheels up to the rear axle the low floor and additional space freed by the redesign initially titled the hlf by hertz greatly reduced loading and unloading time increased convenience and were for a time exclusive to hertz the bus was subsequently marketed as the gillig low floor and is widely deployed by us public transportation agencies heavy equipment rentaledit hertz also maintained a heavy equipment rental division known as the hertz equipment rental corporation aka herc until july   herc started operating in  with its first location in houston tx it was headquartered in park ridge new jersey united states in  hertz announced that they would separate their equipment rental division through a tax free spin off the split was completed on june   and on july   hertz equipment rental corporation became an independently publicly traded company called herc rentals inc herc has more than  branches throughout the united states canada the european union and china referencesedit  hertz global announces kathryn v marinello to become president and chief executive officer irhertzcom retrieved may     hertz says over  jobs to go bbc news january   retrieved december     a b hertz global holdings inc company profile yahoo finance retrieved january      us car rental market auto rental news retrieved may     the hertz corporation history funding universe retrieved may     about hertz company overview irhertzcom retrieved may     a b hertz history hertz corporation retrieved january     andrew ross sorkin september   private investors to buy hertz for  billion new york times retrieved december     hertz acquires used car dealer bca january   retrieved february     stacy collett hertz improves customer experience with friendlier kiosks cio retrieved march     carl icahn is loading up on hertz and shares are popping business insider january      auto rental news december     auto rental news january    hertz names evp of north american rental operations auto rental news august    michael taride forbes april    hertz signs definitive agreement to acquire dollar thrifty press release dollar thrifty automotive group april   archived from the original on january   retrieved august     bliss jeff clothier mark november   avis may have to sell assets to get thrifty proposal bloomberg retrieved november     dollar thrifty takes itself off the market bloomberg businessweek associated press october     moss linda hertz buys dollar thrifty northjerseycom   terlep sharon kendall brent november   hertz to get approval of dollarthrifty deal the wall street journal p b   hertz global holdings inc htz reuters retrieved august     httpwwwoverlandwestcomaboutushtml  nolan bruce  amc amx  hertz rent a racer retrieved december     rentaracer hertz and the muscle car era fossilcars march   retrieved december     grant john  the green marketing manifesto wiley isbn  retrieved january     hopf leo welter william  rethink rei